languages.text: "Хотелось бы, конечно, когда-нибудь глянуть на то место, откуда поставки везут... ну да пустое это. Тут мое место".
"One day, I'd love to see the place where these supplies come from... But, ah, what am I saying? My place is here."

languages.text: 「いつか、供給品がどこから来るのか見てみたいな…でも、ああ、何でもない。私の居場所はここです」

languages.text: « J'aimerais bien voir l'endroit où on fabrique ces produits... Oh, mais qu'est-ce que je raconte ? Ma place est ici. »
languages.original_text: "One day, I'd love to see the place where these supplies come from... But, ah, what am I saying? My place is here."

languages.text: “真希望有一天，我能亲眼看看这些补给品都是从哪里生产出来的……不过，哈，我这是说什么傻话呢？这里才是我该呆的地方。”
languages.original_text: "One day, I'd love to see the place where these supplies come from... But, ah, what am I saying? My place is here."

languages.text: «Algún día me gustaría ver de dónde vienen los suministros... Qué leches, de aquí no me muevo».
languages.original_text: "One day, I'd love to see the place where these supplies come from... But, ah, what am I saying? My place is here."

languages.text: "Irgendwann will ich mal sehen, woher diese Vorräte kommen ... Aber, äh, was rede ich denn da? Ich gehöre hierher."

languages.text: "Bir gün bu erzakların geldiği yeri görmek isterdim... Aman be, benimki de laf. Buraya aitim ben."
